{"tid":1358404,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不如一齊寫信俾天琦","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T02:41:02.000Z","uid":148983,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"90c962472b58762a5217b15f7fa31f2444fb8ad1","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"而家天琦喺監獄入面<br />\n見到越嚟越多人贊同佢嘅理念同上街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該感到好欣慰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如我哋一齊寫信俾佢，叫佢唔好放棄，我哋等佢出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便講多啲新聞都冇講嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>寫信須知</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">【寫信支持梁天琦】<br />\n各位關心天琦的朋友，由 1 月 22 日至今，天琦已遭囚禁一個月，其案件仍在審理當中。早前，多得星火同盟的幫忙，天琦已收到不少朋友的來信。天琦表示，每次收到來信都感到溫暖，每封信之於他都是莫名的鼓勵。從今日起，由天琦好友組成的義工收信小組會開始運作，負責接收廣大市民想寄給天琦的信件。如你希望寄信給天琦，為他打氣，想為他帶來一點溫暖，可依以下指示，將心意送到天琦手上：<br />\n<br />\n【信件收集】<br />\n1. 寄信前請務必確認信件付足郵費，根據郵局政策，不足郵費的信件會被銷毀，為免你的信件送不到天琦手上，千萬要付足郵費<br />\n2. 寄給天琦的信件請寄到義工收信小組的信箱地址：郵政總局郵政信箱 8632 號 P.O. Box 8632, General Post Office<br />\n<br />\n【動筆前須知】<br />\n可寄：<br />\n1. 不大於 A4 的信紙；信紙不一定是白色，但請盡量選素色信紙<br />\n2. 沒有貼上郵票和貼紙的一般明信片。如要寄明信片，請將明信片放入信封寄來，義工會再處理<br />\n3. 畫上圖畫的信紙<br />\n4. 賀卡、生日卡之類，但不可以有音樂、立體、特別剪裁、金粉絲帶等裝飾<br />\n<br />\n不可寄 &mdash;&mdash; 寄了也只能存放在天琦的「私人物件保存處」，直至刑期完結<br />\n1. 日曆<br />\n2. 含有賠率的體育新聞<br />\n3. 直接列印的新聞。如想寄新聞又或評論文章予天琦，請在文章上下寫上專給天琦的訊息，這才會被視為「個人信件」，獲准接收<br />\n4. 貼上郵票和貼紙的紙<br />\n5. 信紙上，不可以有金粉等裝飾<br />\n6. 錢<br />\n7. 郵票<br />\n8. 回郵信封<br />\n9. 小卡紙，如書籤、咭片等 <br />\n10. 仔細描述監內情況的內容<br />\n<br />\n【義工收信小組處理信件程序】<br />\n1. 義工會先打開信封，檢查信件內容，保護天琦個人安全。<br />\n2. 部份信件或會暫時留下，並供天琦日後再讀。<br />\n3. 義工會在每頁信紙寫上天琦在囚編號。<br />\n4. 由於「在囚編號」是個人私隱，義工不會公開，因此才會要求各位寄來讓我們代理。<br />\n5. 義工小組承諾絕對不會外洩任何私隱。<br />\n<br />\n【當信件去到懲教人員手上】<br />\n1. 職員會檢查信件內容符合規定；如信紙有貼紙，貼紙部份會被剪走。<br />\n2. 信封會被扣起，職員只會交信紙給天琦。<br />\n3. 如天琦有原因要取回信封，查看回郵地址，他要先申請；因此，如欲收到回郵，請將你的回郵地址寫在信紙，方便天琦。<br />\n<br />\n【回信】<br />\n基於各種限制，天琦未能一一回信，寄信人很可能收不到回信，敬請見諒。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDBYjmN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDBYjmN.jpg&h=55e3b6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/172224869857024/posts/407452293000946/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F172224869857024%2Fposts%2F407452293000946%2F&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1QwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=dab52d45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/172224869857024/posts/407452293000946/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PsTscGH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPsTscGH.png&h=2af03a75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">7.27元朗見</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"2246f546f94bdffae6310eae61c82dc8206426d3","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da99a2bdc1c2c66529a1804cc5821a7856db559c","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34924d93df84ee131fece9f6046e64809eab03b","tid":1358404,"uid":165246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"4c0928f262ddb41d55e27889a3a58a91814afe49","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec27e8e4f681d3e6c4fdd0017bebd1138fa3e7a","tid":1358404,"uid":71469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f02b0b92430857c9ccb5bb3e3068e4b28678c50","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9726c8168567673cb31f4979a6a53f084d27523","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943b74d594a2e490ad162fa7a536556f07e2e709","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf46d8310d37ca6d179048201c9e35d88f41c412","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ec5f4dfb10df24113d0e735a0f13f7489ad2bc","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e5152405199adc07c2d8ca3fb099aab3268579","tid":1358404,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited